[X-Art] The Red Fox (aka Michelle) (Rope Priorities / 05.11.2014)

Tonight you will see two beautiful people make playful and passionate love to one another. It's a fun role having The Red Fox tied up and at Jake's will this time (I'm remebering her teasing and gliding her pelvis over top of Jake as he looked up at her and wanted a taste in "Feeling Frisky"). Either scenario is super HOT with these two, so make one a priority...and for this one, a Rope Priority
